     k-promo promo-2 iwonder\n                    k-colour-palette-palette-5\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/guides/zs9bwmn\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp square\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x256/p01q7zcp.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01q7zcp\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-header\">How journalists were censored during World War One</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><img src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/80x80/p01q7zy7.jpg\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"type\">Presented by</span><span class=\"name\">Frank Gardner, BBC News</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-3 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/history/world-war-one/10566025/Honoured-the-WW1-pigeons-who-earned-their-wings.html\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01sjkvf.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01sjkvf\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-link\">Visit</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">The war pigeons who earned their wings</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-4 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-hampshire-25147640\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01sjkd5.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01sjkd5\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">The role of dogs in World War One</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-5 gel\"><a href=\"http://royalsignalsmuseum.co.uk/WebSite/\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01sjlt7.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01sjlt7\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite ic